        "lang": "en",
        "text": "Then the elders of his city shall call him and speak to him, and if he persists, saying, ‘I do not wish to take her,’"
      },
      "nasb": {
        "version_id": "NASB",
        "version_name": "New American Standard Bible",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "Then the elders of his city shall summon him and speak to him. And if he persists and says, ‘I do not desire to take her,’"
      },
      "niv": {
        "version_id": "NIV",
        "version_name": "New International Version",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "Then the elders of his town shall summon him and talk to him. If he persists in saying, “I do not want to marry her,”"
      },
      "nkjv": {
        "version_id": "NKJV",
        "version_name": "New King James Version",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "Then the elders of his city shall call him and speak to him. But if he stands firm and says, ‘I do not want to take her,’"
      },
      "nlt": {
        "version_id": "NLT",
        "version_name": "New Living Translation",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "The elders of the town will then summon him and talk with him. If he still refuses and says, ‘I don’t want to marry her,’"
      }
